[SPEAKER_14]: Here, paper 23-458.

122
00:10:13,308 --> 00:10:15,996
[SPEAKER_14]: This is our firefighters.

123
00:10:20,528 --> 00:10:23,469
[SPEAKER_14]: revised wage adjustment.

124
00:10:23,509 --> 00:10:30,012
[SPEAKER_14]: I think they've waited long enough, I believe over 850 days, so if we can hear them sooner rather than later, it would be greatly appreciated.

125
00:10:30,672 --> 00:10:30,932
[SPEAKER_06]: Thank you.

126
00:10:30,952 --> 00:10:36,574
[SPEAKER_06]: So on the motion of Councilor Scarpelli to suspend the rules to take 23-458, seconded by Vice-President Behrs.

127
