[SPEAKER_06]: 12 Dell Avenue petition to amend deed restriction.

344
00:29:20,948 --> 00:29:23,709
[SPEAKER_06]: Petitioners and owners, Gerald L. Alves and Janet R. Alves.

345
00:29:23,729 --> 00:29:31,232
[SPEAKER_06]: We have Attorney Dash before us tonight, I think, with an update, so I'm gonna avoid reading the whole paper, so if you wanna provide us an update.

346
