351
00:29:41,639 --> 00:29:44,400
[SPEAKER_15]: We thought we would have something for you tonight, but we do not.

352
00:29:44,901 --> 00:29:49,604
[SPEAKER_15]: I would note that staff had a very creative idea that came up this afternoon that we'd like to explore.

353
00:29:50,224 --> 00:29:52,906
[SPEAKER_15]: So I know that's your next meeting, so hopefully we'll have it.

354
00:29:52,926 --> 00:29:53,386
[SPEAKER_15]: Yes, that's right.

355
00:29:53,406 --> 00:29:55,208
[SPEAKER_15]: We will have it wrapped up by that point.

356
00:29:56,008 --> 00:29:56,869
[SPEAKER_19]: But that's where we stand.

357
00:29:57,249 --> 00:29:57,549
[SPEAKER_06]: Thank you.

358
00:29:57,809 --> 00:30:00,211
[SPEAKER_19]: Motion to continue to our December 12 meeting.

359
