1074
01:28:55,887 --> 01:29:03,388
[SPEAKER_01]: And part of the reason they can't give it away, because they can't mitigate, I mean, all the damages that have been done by the casino have been mitigated.

1075
01:29:04,229 --> 01:29:10,810
[SPEAKER_01]: And cities and towns are having a, they were trying to get a little more creative on what they thought were damages.

1076
